36
00:02:05,899 --> 00:02:10,099
Ya. Seperti Sherlock Holmes.

37
00:02:11,599 --> 00:02:13,799
Kenapa kau tidak berhenti bersikap terlalu curiga

38
00:02:13,799 --> 00:02:17,899
